  <span id="freeText9355277914906678814" style="display:none">This was entitled "The Fear Index" when I started reading it. Now it is "Angst". WTF? <br /><br />It had a good premise, but there was too much psychology, not enough action. I almost abandoned it several times. Finally there was some action &amp; it made so little sense that I did abandon it. I didn't care too much for the narrator, either.</span>
